<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rby kẖyrk wrḥmẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- rby kẖyrk wrḥmẗ ytbʿạny fy ạlṭryq
 flhdẖạ lst ạ̉kẖsẖy̱ ạ̉y ʿwz ạ̉y ḍyq
 qrạr- ạrfʿ qlby ạ̹lyk wạ̉gẖny fy ạlḥyạẗ
 ạ̉nt kẖyry wạ̹lhy wkẖlạṣy wạlnjạẗ
 2- tsmʿny kl ywm ṣwtk ạlḥạny ạlrqyq
 fy ḥdytẖ ysyr qlby yʿṭy ạ̉mnaⁿạ wtẖyq
 3- ạ̉nt tṣgẖy bạhtmạm fy ạ̉nyny wạlậlạm
 wtzyl kl kẖwfy tmlạny bạlslạm
 4- ạ̉wdʿ ʿmry ldyk yạ rfyqy fy ạlmsyr
 lys ly kẖl ạ̉myn mtẖlk mʿy ysyr</lyrics>
